----------------
  Code: AguileraRodriguez2025
  Paradigm: imagery
  DOI: 10.1038/s41597-025-05926-5
  Subjects: 15
  Sessions per subject: 2
  Events: avanzar=1, retroceder=2, derecha=3, izquierda=4
  Trial interval: [0, 2] s
  File format: EDF

